Interface NumericInputDialogPrimitive

  • All Superinterfaces:
    InputPrimitive, Primitive
    public interface NumericInputDialogPrimitive
extends InputPrimitive
    An interface representing a numeric input input dialog (NID) primitive.

    This primitive has type Primitive.PrimitiveType.NID.

    The allowed input format is InputPrimitive.InputFormat.DIGIT.
